text:
Hi James,

The delta was about $100k.  However  last week I learned that we now have a GTM partner for PAM and the current plan is that they will do the design refinement.  I am just back from vacation and working through the details so if gaps remain – I’ll be sure to reach out.  We are just kicking off discussions so if there are pieces we do need help with – I’ll be sure to reach out.  As Aaren said, we loved your team’s ideas and enthusiasm for the project.

Thanks to you, Lynsey and the team for the proposal and effort to date.  I hope we get the opportunity to work together in the future.
Katie
^^ cheers to all of you and thanks for your hard work, even if owls was not meant to be. :slightly_smiling_face:
while this wasn’t meant to be, I believe we can all look back at work and feel proud of what we did for this proposal
i can’t wait to work with this team on something that is a better fit!
bummer though, you all did a great job. loved that visual proposal. I just hope they keep these toys   s m a l l   !
i still want to see the scary 3 foot wolf.
But honestly will always have <@U0GN0A9EV>’s impersonation of it in my head, which is probably better anyway.
Bummed about the outcome though - and agree it was an extremely well-done pitch.
